{"article_id":"QPtk6a6TmJAq7LHl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In Fight With 'Chuck And Nancy , '","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Trump Says","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"He 'd Be 'Proud ' To Shut Down Government","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"In a testy Oval Office exchange with the two top congressional Democrats , Rep. Nancy Pelosi and Sen. Chuck Schumer , President Trump made clear","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"he would be `` proud '' to shut down the government in less than two weeks","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"if he does n't get funding for his border wall .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"`` I 'll be the one","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to shut it down .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"I will take the mantle .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"And I will shut it down for border security , ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Trump told House and Senate Democratic leaders","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"as Vice President Pence sat by stoically .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The statement from Trump came in an extraordinary show before the cameras and the press , with minutes of tense back-and-forth with both Pelosi , the likely incoming House speaker , and Schumer , the Senate minority leader .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"Democratic leaders have made it clear","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"they do n't intend to give the president a victory on funding for his signature border wall ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and afterward they released a statement","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"reiterating","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"that `` We gave the president two options","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that would keep the government open .","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"It 's his choice","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"to accept one of those options","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"or shut the government down . ''","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"Pelosi told reporters on Capitol Hill at a holiday reception later Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"she and Trump had spoken on the phone","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"but there was no response to the earlier offer from her and Schumer .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"According to an aide ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"the call was around 4 p.m.","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and lasted about a minute .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"Speaking immediately after the meeting ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"both Schumer and Pelosi thought","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"they had emerged with the upper hand","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"after seemingly baiting Trump into taking the blame","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"if there 's a partial shutdown just days before Christmas .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"`` This Trump shutdown , this temper tantrum","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"he seems to want to throw ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"will not get him his wall , ''","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"the Senate minority leader told reporters outside the White House .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Throughout the meeting , Trump kept insisting","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that much of the wall has already been built","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"( numerous fact-checkers earlier this year determined","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"it has n't ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"which Schumer pointed out )","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and he has also said","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that the military can build the rest .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"In a statement","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"provided to NPR Tuesday evening ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"a spokesperson for the Department of Defense said","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"`` to date , there is no plan","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to build sections of the wall . ''","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"But `` Congress has provided options under [ existing law ]","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that could permit the Department of Defense to fund border barrier projects , such as in support of counter drug operations or national emergencies . ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"During the 2016 campaign , Trump also kept claiming","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that Mexico would pay","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"to build the wall ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"but he has since dropped that talking point .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Pelosi insisted during the meeting","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that the cameras should leave ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"saying afterward","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"she made such a request","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"because `` we did n't want to contradict the president","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"when he was putting forth figures","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"that have no basis in fact .","depth":14},{"id":62,"text":"... I did n't want to say in front of those people ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"'You have no idea what you 're talking about . ' ``","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Except by making that comment","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"just after leaving the Oval Office ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Pelosi was saying just that .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"She also kept trying to explain to Trump","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"that there was n't enough support even in the GOP-controlled House for his border wall ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"urging him to accept a continuous funding resolution at the current spending levels , or $ 1.3 billion for a year .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"But Trump kept interjecting to shift blame ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"a House vote would n't matter","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"since he needs to get to 60 votes in the Senate anyway","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"and that would require help from Democrats","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"- a frequent complaint of his .","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"Back on Capitol Hill , Pelosi told fellow Democratic lawmakers in private","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that she was `` trying to be the mom '' in the room .","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"`` I ca n't explain it to you .","depth":17},{"id":79,"text":"It was so wild .","depth":17},{"id":80,"text":"It goes to show you :","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"You get into a tinkle contest with a skunk ,","depth":18},{"id":82,"text":"you get tinkle all over you , ''","depth":18},{"id":83,"text":"Pelosi said ,","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"according to an aide in the room .","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"`` You ca n't let him take you down that path .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"But the fact is","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"we did get him to say , to fully own","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"that the shutdown was his .","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"That was an accomplishment . ''","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"In another comment","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"sure to irk the president ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"Pelosi went even further ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"that Trump 's obsession with the border wall is `` like a manhood thing for him .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"As if manhood could ever be associated with him . ''","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"The tense exchanges underscored the challenges in the coming two years of divided government .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Trump diverted from discussing Democrats ' takeover of the House ,","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"choosing to focus on GOP gains in the Senate","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"- thanks , in large part , to a very Republican-friendly map in the 2018 midterms .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"`` When the president brags","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"that he won North Dakota and Indiana ,","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"he 's in real trouble , ''","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"Schumer jabbed .","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"The White House tried to paint a very different picture of the meeting after the fact ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"with press secretary Sarah Sanders saying in a statement ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"`` President Trump had a constructive dialogue with Democrat Leaders Chuck Schumer and Nancy Pelosi , ''","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"although `` Major disagreement remains on the issue of border security and transparency . ''","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Trump himself told reporters later on Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"that `` believe it or not ,","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"I think","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"it was a very friendly meeting .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"... I 've actually liked [ Schumer and Pelosi ] for a long period of time ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"and I respect them both ''","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"and that ``","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"when the press left ,","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"we had a fairly long meeting","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"and we really discussed a lot of great subjects . ''","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"And the president showed no regrets","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"for having said","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"he would own a shutdown","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"if it comes to that .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"`` If we close down the country","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"I will take it ,","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"because we 're closing it down for border security ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"and I think","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"I win that every single time , ''","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Speaking on Capitol Hill ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , acknowledged","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"it had been a `` spirited meeting '' at the White House ,","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"but that `` I 'd still like to have a smooth ending here ''","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"and avoid a government shutdown .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"`` I 'm sort of hoping for a Christmas miracle here","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"that we 'll have a level of cooperation","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"that we do n't normally have","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"in getting bills across the Senate floor , ''","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"McConnell said ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"pointing to not just the government funding bill but the farm bill and a criminal justice overhaul .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Democratic resistance to funding the wall may have prompted Trump 's pre-meeting tweetstorm ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"which over a series of five long tweets seemed to simultaneously concede defeat and declare victory on wall funding .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"Troops have been stationed along the Southern border with Mexico since just before the midterm elections ,","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"while some are being extended through the end of January ,","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"other units have been sent home .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"`` He 's talking about reprogramming/transferring funds from other [ Department of Defense ] programs , ''","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"said Stan Collender , a federal budget expert ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"when asked","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"if he could explain the Trump tweets .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"`` That would indeed take away resources from other activities . ''","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"Collender said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"he was n't sure how much discretion Trump would actually have to do this","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"it will `` get the new Democratic House very angry . ''","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"Even before the Tuesday morning tweetstorm , in recent days Trump had been far less specific about his demands for border wall funding","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"than he has been in past rounds of budget talks .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"Sometimes he leaves out specific dollar amounts","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"( though the standing request is $ 5 billion ) .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"And his use of the phrase `` border security '' indicates more than just funding","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"to build the wall .","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"`` Congress must fully fund border security in the year-ending funding bill , ''","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"Trump said Friday in a speech at a law enforcement conference .","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"`` We have to -","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"we have to get this done .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"They 're playing games .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"They 're playing political games .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"I actually think","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"the politics of what they 're doing is very bad for them ,","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"but we 're going to very soon find out .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"Maybe I 'm not right ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"but usually I 'm right . ''","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"looking at public opinion ,","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"may feel","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"they have some leverage in the talks .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"A new NPR/PBS NewsHour/Marist Poll out Tuesday shows","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"that 57 percent of Americans ,","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"including 63 percent of independents ,","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"want the president to compromise on the border wall","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"to prevent gridlock","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"and not risk a government shutdown .","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"Two-thirds of Republicans , however , want the president to stand his ground .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"And Trump is often laser-focused on his base .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"The days of high expectations for White House summits","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"leading to bipartisan breakthroughs","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"were well in the past","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"even before Tuesday 's Oval Office throw down .","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"A little more than a year ago , Trump had a couple of meetings with Schumer and Pelosi .","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"he had worked out a deal on immigration with `` Chuck and Nancy , ''","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"as he called them .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"`` I think","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"something can happen , ''","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"`` We 'll see what happens .","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"But something will happen . ''","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"Nothing happened .","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"The deal blew up","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"without even an agreement on what the deal was .","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"The sparring between Trump , Pelosi and Schumer may well be a preview of the next two years of divided government .","depth":4},{"id":200,"text":"Both Trump and Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"who is expected to once again become speaker","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"when Democrats take control of the House ,","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"have talked about the potential for bipartisan compromise on things like infrastructure and prescription drug prices .","depth":7},{"id":204,"text":"But they 've also both foreshadowed conflict .","depth":7},{"id":205,"text":"Pelosi and Democrats are promising robust investigations of Trump and his administration ,","depth":8},{"id":206,"text":"and Trump has said","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"that would lead to a `` warlike posture . '' `` Then at the end of two years , nothing is done , ''","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"Trump predicted .","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"`` Now what 's bad for them is being in the majority ;","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"I 'm just going to blame them . ''","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"This leaves many questions :","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"Are Democrats willing or able to compromise with Trump ?","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"Is Trump willing to deal ?","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"If he is ,","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"will congressional Republicans go along ?","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"given the way","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"Trump has changed his mind in the midst of past negotiations ,","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"will anyone trust him ?","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"Still , allies of the president and Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":221,"text":"interviewed for this story","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"say","depth":7},{"id":223,"text":"some limited compromise is possible .","depth":6},{"id":224,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"there 's several positions","depth":10},{"id":226,"text":"the president has","depth":10},{"id":227,"text":"that frankly line up more traditionally with Democrats , ''","depth":9},{"id":228,"text":"said Marc Short , former director of legislative affairs for the Trump administration .","depth":7},{"id":229,"text":"`` The question","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"that is yet to be determined","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"is whether or not Democrats will give their leadership the flexibility","depth":9},{"id":233,"text":"to negotiate with the president . ''","depth":9},{"id":234,"text":"That 's one way","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"of pinning blame back on the other party","depth":9},{"id":236,"text":"when big things fail to get done .","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"Short also questioned","depth":6},{"id":238,"text":"whether Democrats would be willing to give Trump a win","depth":7},{"id":239,"text":"as he begins his re-election campaign in earnest .","depth":7},{"id":240,"text":"John Lawrence , a former chief of staff to Pelosi , countered","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"that Democrats are likely open","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"and looking to cut some deals .","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"`` [ Pelosi ] is going to be ,","depth":10},{"id":244,"text":"and I think","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"Democrats in the House are going to be ,","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"concerned with proving","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"that they can be trusted","depth":11},{"id":248,"text":"that they can govern , ''","depth":11},{"id":249,"text":"Lawrence said .","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"Short and Lawrence both see incentives","depth":9},{"id":251,"text":"for their respective parties to get something done ,","depth":9},{"id":252,"text":"while questioning","depth":9},{"id":253,"text":"whether those incentives exist for the other side .","depth":9},{"id":254,"text":"But first they have to make it to next year .","depth":8},{"id":255,"text":"And the budget fight","depth":10},{"id":256,"text":"brewing","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"as 2018 closes out","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"could well affect the relationship going forward .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":517,"left":261,"right":516,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":0,"right":260,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":516,"left":456,"right":515,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":456,"left":270,"right":455,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":269,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":263,"right":268,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":3,"right":262,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":266,"right":267,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":264,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":455,"left":311,"right":454,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":311,"left":293,"right":310,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":271,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":283,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":277,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":15,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":16,"right":275,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":275,"left":272,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":19,"right":273,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":279,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":22,"right":278,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":25,"right":280,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":287,"right":290,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":285,"right":286,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":284,"right":30,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":289,"right":36,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":288,"right":35,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":33,"right":34,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":306,"right":309,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":299,"right":305,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":297,"right":298,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":37,"right":296,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":38,"right":295,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":39,"right":294,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":303,"right":304,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":301,"right":302,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":301,"left":300,"right":46,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":308,"right":54,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":51,"right":307,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":454,"left":409,"right":453,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":409,"left":394,"right":408,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":394,"left":359,"right":393,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":359,"left":322,"right":358,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":322,"left":319,"right":321,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":319,"left":312,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":318,"left":313,"right":317,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":313,"left":57,"right":58,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":317,"left":315,"right":316,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN